{"title":"小白花——丙辰清明四周年祭","authors":["项南"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":3,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"小白花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——丙辰清明四周年祭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"项南"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我度过几十个严冬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见过无数次大雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都没有给我留下多少记忆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有一场大雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我的一生中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么也不会忘记。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这场漫天大雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一夜之间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洒白了整个大地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这哪里是雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是朵朵小白花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怒开在清明时节。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银花似海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银花如雪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"低吟声处可以听到惊雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悲歌是发自内心的抗议。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小白花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你成了战士手中最有力的武器。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一朵花，一个心意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一朵花，一滴眼泪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小白花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分担了人们的悲痛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小白花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"揭穿了人间的鬼蜮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我读过天方夜谭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听过各种传说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都没有发现过这种奇迹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门前这场大雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重新燃起了希望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天又回到了大地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开吧！小白花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿你越开越茂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下吧！漫天的大雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿你越下越密。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史已经不可逆转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管还有多大的阻力！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}